description:
This is a 12 minute workout called '8 Bodyweight Exercises EVERYONE Should Do! (Hit Every Muscle)' from the channel Tone and Tighten.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Progression Quest and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: 8 of the best bodyweight exercises to tone and strengthen your muscles at home. Includes beginner, intermediate, and advanced options for upper body, lower body, and core exercises to maximize your results. Keep reading for links mentioned in the video!

No gym membership? No equipment? NO PROBLEM!

You don’t need weights, pulleys, or bands to get in a great strength-training workout. In fact when performed correctly, the right bodyweight exercises can yield similar gains in strength and muscle tone as performing resisted training in the gym.
